body:
read it on the AO3 at https://ift.tt/2OyCifH

by cmajorchords

“Why did the coffee file a police report?”

Yoongi twitches. He can’t help it. “.. Why?” he asks wearily, wondering if this counts as enough reason to ask for a raise.

“Because it got mugged,” the guy tells him with obvious, poorly disguised glee, and then collapses over the counter in a fit of squeaky laughter that should not be as endearing as Yoongi finds it. It really shouldn’t be. None of this guy’s jokes are funny, he just keeps coming in and saying them and he always orders fries with a milkshake and then dips the fries into the milkshake, he dresses like Ronald McDonald meets horrible confetti factory accident, and none of this should be attractive. None of this at all.

or; yoongi works the night shift at a fast food joint and he really shouldn’t be so attracted to this beautiful man who keeps coming in at three in the morning and making terrible puns. he doesn’t even know his name.
